{"tid":1988585,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大阪市長指女士愛亂逛街 倡男士去採購被轟","createTime":"2020-04-25T10:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T04:21:35.000Z","uid":28114,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"26149a0f3916f66149d39155f78ee00223ab888f","tid":1988585,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/facebook_20200425-CH-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB3-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2Ffacebook_20200425-CH-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB3-1.jpg&h=bc83ca35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「女士買東西猶豫不決，花很久的時間」<br />\n<br />\n女士是天生購物狂？日本大阪市長松井一郎建議在新冠肺炎疫情下，由男士出門採購日用品，因為「女士買東西猶豫不決，花很久的時間」。此言一出，立刻引來隆隆炮聲，認為他對女士充滿偏見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200425-CH-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200425-CH-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB1.jpg&h=a8491ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大阪市長松井一郎建議由男性出門採購。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n56歲的松井一郎提出，男人應負責買東西，因為女人會買很久，她們會逛來逛去。他還說，跟男人說要買甚麼，他們會拿了就走，因此最好由他們外出購物，可減少人群接觸。松井一郎承認，他的言論可能會被視為落伍，但他堅持他家確實是如此。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200425-CH-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200425-CH-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB3.jpg&h=ea6c1dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大阪市長認爲女士外出比男士花時間。AP圖片<br />\n<br />\n松井一郎認爲，男士顧客店內購物時間相對較短，從而減少了病毒的潛在傳播風險。松井還有說應該限制去超市購物的頻率，並建議出生月份為雙數的人雙數日去，出生月份為單數的人單數日去。"},{"pid":"693f75c62dd6f5aee4c3169ce09d3cbf76f2a837","tid":1988585,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"96043a3b0c83ee26435b79d0cdab3bc612e39667","tid":1988585,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200425-CH-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200425-CH-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB2.jpg&h=26c61d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大阪市長松井一郎建議由男性出門採購。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n松井呼籲民衆採取措施降低病毒感染風險，但有關性別的言論卻引發不小的爭議，其中令女士尤為不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200425-CH-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200425-CH-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB4.jpg&h=e0a914dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大阪市長認爲女士外出比男士花時間。AP圖片<br />\n<br />\n日本女記者江川紹子在Twitter稱：「希望這些對日常生活一無所知的人，不要拍腦袋一想就發表評論。」也有人說，這種話不應由公職人員來說，為什麼公職人員就不明白呢？「自己想到什麼就脫口而出，還請市長自我反省。」"},{"pid":"38c5024aed8190e06eb2e35f88176e4ddb0c43cb","tid":1988585,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"佢冇講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aba39810a6eecb816846ee1745b23f7658ed1c9","tid":1988585,"uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"013bd47fdfd8d1af45db4d578f90612c23cca5fc","tid":1988585,"uid":149035,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />